The infusion pump systems, accessories, and software market is segmented based on product, type, application, and end-user. In terms of products, the market includes devices, infusion pump software, and accessories. The types of infusion pumps in the market are volumetric infusion pumps, syringe infusion pumps, ambulatory infusion pumps, enteral infusion pumps, and patient-controlled analgesia pumps. These pumps find applications in various medical fields such as chemotherapy, diabetes treatment, treating gastrointestinal diseases, pediatrics, hematology, analgesia, nutrition delivery, and others. The end-users of infusion pump systems, accessories, and software include hospitals, ambulatory surgical centers, specialty clinics, and homecare settings.

